title: 3-Way Thermostatic Valve Shower Mixer Square Knobs Matte Black
description: Modern square knobs and a sleek appearance make this easy-to-install single-panel shower mixer a perfect choice. Equipped with a 3-way shower diverter, this brass thermostatic shower valve mixer by ALFI brand lets you switch from your handheld shower head or above shower head to tub filler or body jets any time you wish. It comes in three stylish finishes to accommodate your bathroom style, Black Matte, Polished Chrome, and Brushed Nickel. Additional Information FEATURE 1 Solid brass construction coated with a Polished Chrome or Brushed Nickel finish. FEATURE 2 A 3-way diverter is typically used for an above showerhead, a hand-held showerhead, and the third for either a tub filler or body jets. If you only need 2-ways, your plumber can easily cap the third pipe to cancel it out. FEATURE 3 A thermostatic valve allows you to have separate temperature and pressure controls, allowing you to leave the water at a certain temperature and turn your water on and off separately. FEATURE 4 Three square knobs from top to bottom: Water Diverter, Temperature Control, and On/Off Control. FEATURE 5 Sleek modern design FEATURE 6 Single panel design makes it a breeze to install on any surface. FEATURE 7 Certified by Uniform Plumbing Code (cUPC). UPC logo of authenticity etched on the unit. FEATURE 8 Shower options and Hot & Cold functions etched on the plate FEATURE 9 Includes both the trim and the rough-in valve, so it has everything needed to function. FEATURE 10 The Diverter knob can be positioned halfway between outlets, giving you the opportunity to indulge in two shower experiences simultaneously.
